Package: SafeMerge
Type: Package
Title: SAFER MERGING OF TWO DATA FRAMES.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Olivier", "Humblet", , "ohumblet@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A wrapper for the merge function, for interactive use. Prints information and warnings about the merge, then conducts the merge in question (with nearly identical functionality, except as described in the SafeMerge function documentation).
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr
Imports: dplyr,
    magrittr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
